---
title: Turkey Scallopine Florentine with Tomato Linguine
description: The classic Italian combination of spinach and cheese tops this tender turkey, turning golden brown in the oven. Lemony linguine perks up this rich and satisfying dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/turkey-scallopine-florentine-ae518752.jpg
